Help.add-autoline: Add new channel to autoline system.
Help.add-suggestion: Add new channel to suggestion system.
Help.add-tax: Add new channel to tax system.
Help.add-feedback: Add new channel to feedback system.
Help.lock: Disables @everyone from sending messages in specific channel.
Help.mute: Mute a member from text channels so they cannot type.
Help.role: Add/remove a role(s) for a user.
Help.timeout: Timeout a user from sending messages, react or join voice channels.
Help.unlock: Allows @everyone to send messages in specific channel.
Help.avatar: Display your's avatar or someone else's avatar.
Help.banner: Display your's banner or someone else's banner.
Help.roles: Get a list of server roles.
Help.apply-admin: Set pecific role of submissions admin.
Help.dm-mode: Set DM messages mode on apply accept or reject.
Help.say: Send a specific message to a specific channel.
Help.embed: Send a specific embed message to a specific channel.
Help.send: Send a specific message to a specific member.
Help.come: request someone to come to the channel.
